Package ca.phon.query.db

Interface ResultSet

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<Result>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    XMLLazyResultSet, XMLResultSet
    public interface ResultSet
extends Iterable<Result>
    Interface for a set of results from a Phon query.
